{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/h1.png?t=1730551869\" />Welcome to the sequel of Mystery Box! Turn wheels, move handles, push buttons, and think smart to solve the puzzles, unlock all the boxes, and collect tiles to discover lost artifacts. You can find hidden tiles on the side of the boxes as well, so pay attention to the details!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/1.gif?t=1730551869\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/h4.png?t=1730551869\" />Discover all Artifacts in this escape room game to unlock an extra amazing level, the Ghost Box!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/h2.png?t=1730551869\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/gb.gif?t=1730551869\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/h3.png?t=1730551869\" />Drag the mouse to walk around each puzzle box, and feel like you're trapped in a room for real</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/h4.png?t=1730551869\" />Once you open all 8 boxes of a chosen pack (and you also collected the small hidden puzzle tiles on the side of the boxes), you'll be able to compose a puzzle and discover a brief history of an artifact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/3.gif?t=1730551869\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/h5.png?t=1730551869\" />Think outside of the box to solve all the puzzles, it's not always easy, but I know you can escape the rooms! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/4.gif?t=1730551869\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/h8.png?t=1730551869\" />Play the game with your headphones on, and get totally immersed in the adventure! Each Box Pack has its music theme, so your escape room experience will be unique</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/h7.png?t=1730551869\" />In case you get stuck while trying to solve a riddle, click the bulb button to get a hint that will help you solve the puzzle you're blocked to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/h8.png?t=1730551869\" />Can you complete all the achievements of this game? Every time you complete a Box Pack, you'll earn its special <i><strong>Steam Achievement</strong></i>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't forget to show your results to the community and spread the word with your friends, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">they may want to compete with you ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/ach.png?t=1730551869\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/xslogo.png?t=1730551869\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>XSGames</strong> is a solo indie game developer from Italy. I self-published the first Mystery Box chapter on the app stores in 2021 and was amazed by its awesome success with mobile game players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Such results changed my life, so I hope you'll enjoy playing the <strong>Mystery Box</strong> escape room adventures as much as I love making them!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ghost Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2541380/9b3f908e1db6f5e0a1d99ae56b5f8cee7a4599d5.jpg"},{"name":"Chinese Boxes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2541380/44c4e9c088768cb5ebf51c7be147acab84843245.jpg"},{"name":"Celtic Boxes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2541380/787fbe8c4a3126564d73c6346c8fe599f3d2ca84.jpg"},{"name":"Viking Boxes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2541380/020b0d982e14135309fadcf6e46abbf9b1ef8e0a.jpg"},{"name":"Egyptian Boxes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2541380/1e521bdeaf18a6b07bf47aaa160d54bcd531bfe3.jpg"},{"name":"Greek Boxes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2541380/e7227ae30b6dd7a6b0c4adb831adcb3f70476295.jpg"},{"name":"Aztec Boxes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2541380/db420fedd42b21faf7f1d423e0775b4e8643dcd7.jpg"},{"name":"Amerindian Boxes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2541380/5466ebd0be1b1f1bbf94f90dd3b514cc76072dcc.jpg"}],"total":8},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=17305