lete all the achievements of this game? Every time you complete a Box Pack, you'll earn its special <i><strong>Steam Achievement</strong></i>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't forget to show your results to the community and spread the word with your friends, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">they may want to compete with you ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/ach.png?t=1730551869\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/extras/xslogo.png?t=1730551869\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>XSGames</strong> is a solo indie game developer from Italy. I self-published the first Mystery Box chapter on the app stores in 2021 and was amazed by its awesome success with mobile game players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Such results changed my life, so I hope you'll enjoy playing the <strong>Mystery Box</strong> escape room adventures as much as I love making them!</p>","developers":["XSGames"],"dlc":[2541700],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541380/header.jpg?t=1730551869","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a92024 XSGames. All Rights Reserved","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> 10.15, or later<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel x86 + Apple silicon (64bit OS required)<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> AMD or Intel Integrate